      <title>逃往朝鲜的美国士兵承认叛逃罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/us-soldier-who-bolted-to-north-korea-pleads-guilty-to-desertion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名从韩国越境进入朝鲜的美国陆军士兵承认了五项指控，包括逃兵和不服从长官，被判处一年监禁，他的律师在一份声明中说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/us-soldier-who-bolted-to-north-korea-pleads-guilty-to-desertion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 01:59:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡选举竞争激烈，IMF资金面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/sri-lankans-vote-in-tight-race-that-puts-imf-funding-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡 1,700 万选民于本周六前往投票站选举新总统。两年前，该国遭遇经济崩溃和历史性债务违约，导致大规模政治动荡，前强人领导人下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/sri-lankans-vote-in-tight-race-that-puts-imf-funding-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚计划今年完成与美国的关键矿产协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/australia-eyes-completion-of-us-critical-minerals-pact-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯表示，澳大利亚有望在今年年底前与美国就关键矿产达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/australia-eyes-completion-of-us-critical-minerals-pact-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 00:16:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰外长寻求美国对乌克兰采取“更大胆”的态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/polish-foreign-minister-seeks-braver-us-approach-to-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰最高外交官周五向彭博新闻社表示，乌克兰防御俄罗斯的成功前景可能取决于“拜登政府是否会更加勇敢”，并在下一任美国总统大选和就职之间提供决定性的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/polish-foreign-minister-seeks-braver-us-approach-to-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 23:21:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 跌跌撞撞地迎来了本应属于他的重大胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/keir-starmer-stumbles-into-what-should-be-his-big-victory-lap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党丑闻连年不断，凯尔·史塔默向英国选民承诺，工党将把公共服务置于“使命主导型”政府的核心地位。上任仅两个月，他的首相生涯就陷入了政治捐赠者、免费赠品和员工争执等尴尬故事中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/keir-starmer-stumbles-into-what-should-be-his-big-victory-lap</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国依赖盟友的造船实力与中国竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/us-leans-on-shipbuilding-prowess-of-allies-to-compete-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在任何与中国发生的高风险军事冲突中，美国海军都是取胜的关键。但美国的造船业远远不能满足海军的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/us-leans-on-shipbuilding-prowess-of-allies-to-compete-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马里关闭首都牲畜市场以遏制圣战威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/mali-shuts-cattle-markets-in-capital-in-bid-to-contain-jihadist-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在伊斯兰激进分子发动一系列致命袭击之后，马里关闭了其首都的牲畜市场，据信这些激进分子招募了与牲畜贸易有关的族群的成员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/mali-shuts-cattle-markets-in-capital-in-bid-to-contain-jihadist-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 21:51:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北卡罗来纳州州长称罗宾逊风波可能使哈里斯受益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/north-carolina-governor-says-robinson-furor-could-benefit-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北卡罗来纳州州长罗伊·库珀表示，围绕副州长马克·罗宾逊的争议可能会帮助副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在选举日将他的州推向民主党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/north-carolina-governor-says-robinson-furor-could-benefit-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 21:41:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥贩毒集团头目之子在美国被判贩毒罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-20/urgent-mexican-cartel-leader-s-son-convicted-of-violent-role-in-drug-trafficking-plot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（美联社）——墨西哥贩毒集团头目之子周五被判有罪，他被指控使用暴力，包括致命击落一架军用直升机，帮助其父亲经营该国最大、最危险的贩毒组织之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-20/urgent-mexican-cartel-leader-s-son-convicted-of-violent-role-in-drug-trafficking-plot</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 20:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南卡罗来纳州 13 年来首次执行死刑，一名囚犯被注射死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-20/south-carolina-prepares-for-first-execution-in-13-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚，南卡罗来纳州（美联社）——南卡罗来纳州于周五执行了囚犯弗雷迪·欧文斯的死刑，由于监狱官员无法获得注射死刑所需的药物，该州在意外暂停了 13 年后重新开始执行死刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-20/south-carolina-prepares-for-first-execution-in-13-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 04:03:04 GMT</pubDate>
